4.5. UCF-101 

UCF-101 (Soomro et al., 2012) is an action classification 
dataset with 13,320 videos from 101 different classes. We 
train unconditional VideoGPT models on 16 frame 64 ? 64 
and 128 ? 128 videos, where the original videos have their 
shorter side scaled to 128 pixels, and then center cropped.
